FILE: secret.rs
MOD: identity/secret
ROLE: Crypto primitives — SHA-256 key hashing and hash verification
EP: hash_key; verify_key_hash; ensure_broker_secret
STAB: stable
INV:
  - hash_key produces a hex-encoded SHA-256 digest — deterministic, no salt (known limitation ARCH-05)
  - verify_key_hash re-hashes the input and compares — constant-time comparison not guaranteed (known limitation)
  - ensure_broker_secret reads/creates ~/.agent-broker/broker.key — used at daemon startup only
  - No network, no DB, no stanza concerns
CHK: No callers outside db container — arch fitness identity-callers rule enforces this
